description: A Taste of the Philippines' goal is to put Filipino food on the streets of Denver. We believe in using local products mixed with authentic Filipino ingredients to stay true to authentic recipes. A Taste of the Philippines' goal is to put the Philippines on the map by sharing some of the culture through Filipino food. We offer some of the classic dishes such as chicken adobo, pancit (vegetarian), bistek Tagalog, manok sa gata and ginulayang tofu/manok/shrimp (vegetable stir fry with either tofu, chicken or shrimp. Of course we serve lumpia (beef and vegetarian lumpias available).
name: A Taste of the Philippines
